high_descs: Walk towards the counter in front
Grab a knife from the counter
Walk with the knife towards round table
Slice the bread on the table
Walk towards the microwave
Open the microwave and put knife in there
Walk towards the round table
Grab a piece of bread from the table
Walk towards the microwave open it
Cook the slice, take the slice of bread out of the microwave
Walk towards the round table
Put the slice of cook bread on the table
anns.task_desc: Slice the bread, cook a slice put it on the table

high_descs: Go toward the oven, turn right, turn left, go to the counter with the knives, and turn right.
Take a knife from the counter.
Turn right, go to the far counter, turn right, go toward the round table, turn left, go to the table, and turn right.
Slice the bread on the round table.
Turn right, go around the round table, turn left, turn right, and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the knife in the microwave, and close the microwave.
Turn right, go to the oven, turn right, and go to the round table.
Take a slice of bread from the round table.
Turn right, go around the round table, turn left, turn right, and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the bread in the microwave, close the microwave, run the microwave for two seconds, open the microwave, take the bread from the microwave, and close the microwave.
Turn right, go to the oven, turn right, and go to the round table.
Put the bread on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of warmed bread on the table.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn right to face the kitchen counter just left of the sink
Pick up the knife furthest from the edge of the counter
Turn right and walk over to the round wooden table
Use the knife to cut the loaf of bread on the table
Turn right and walk over to the microwave
Open the microwave and put the knife in it
Turn around and walk back over to the round table
Pick up a slice of bread from the table
Turn right and walk back to the microwave
Heat the bread in the microwave then remove it
Turn around and walk over to the round table
Put the piece of bread on the table by the loaf
anns.task_desc: Put the heated piece of bread on the table
